                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, P</hi> 128.) I took the prisoner on 30th May, at the chapel door, in Trinity-street.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. The book this girl says she saw me take from theseat was my own; I offered to assist the policeman in any way.</p>
